⚙️ Installation

1. Clone this repository
```bash
git clone https://github.com/PrinceKushwaha01/sc-radar-system.git

2. Open Arduino file: firmware/sc_radar_system.ino
-Install required libraries:
-WiFiS3
-Servo
-U8g2
-Upload code to Arduino UNO R4 WiFi
-Open Serial Monitor and get IP address
-Open browser: http://YOUR_DEVICE_IP

🌐 Web Dashboard

The system provides a live web interface with:

Radar-style visualization
Object distance tracking
Real-time updates
Start / Stop controls
